            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, cut your<strong> lime</strong>[s] in half</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and shred finely</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> tomato paste </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>in 75ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [110ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-2-1679389580830-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
