          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-2-1679389580830-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>chicken tinga</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-2-1679389589605-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
