            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through the <strong>drained black beans</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>beany rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
