    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>beany rice </strong>in bowls with the<strong> chicken tinga</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> grated cheese </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>lime mayo </strong>and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
